direction: right

F: "Complex FFT frame\nIn: ADC/FFT cube\nOut: frame[t,rx,chirp/bin]"
P: "Preprocess frame\nIn: complex frame\nOut: clutter-reduced profile + spectral history"
D: "Detect candidate bins\nIn: preprocessed profile\nOut: candidate points (range/xyz/zone/conf)"
T: "Track best target\nIn: candidates + previous track\nOut: stable target (xyz/bin/vz/conf)"
V: "Extract vital micro-features\nIn: spectral history + tracked bin\nOut: micro-state + periodicity features"
A: "Estimate activity\nIn: tracked target + micro-state + motion_level\nOut: occupancy + posture + motion_score"
RX: "Extract respiration signal\nIn: tracked bin + spectral history\nOut: live signal + derivative + quality"
RA: "Analyze respiration metrics\nIn: respiration signal\nOut: RR + apnea + cycle metrics"
O: "Emit EngineOutput\nOut: typed activity + respiration + tracking bundle"

F -> P -> D -> T
T -> V -> O
T -> A -> O
T -> RX -> RA -> O

N1: "Preprocess gate:\nblock downstream until warmup_frames completes."
N2: "Detection gate (concept):\ncandidate if magnitude(bin) > threshold and zone is valid."
N3: "Tracking gate:\nonly stable confirmed target feeds activity/respiration."
N4: "Respiration gate:\nrequires spectral history and confirmed bin lock."
N5: "Motion formula:\nmotion_score = clamp(motion_level / restless_max, 0, 1)."

P -> N1
D -> N2
T -> N3
RX -> N4
A -> N5
